RATIFICATION OF A UNITED NATIONS CONVENTION - 
RATIFICATION D'UNE CONVENTION DES NATIONS UNIES

Authority to ratify the UNITED NATIONS CONVENTION AGAINST CORRUPTION, signed by Canada on May 21, 2004, to provide a global mechanism to prevent and combat corruption.
